title: The Keiser Report No. 150 - May 26 TH [sebaygo1]

The Keiser Report  No. 149
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Thursday, 26 May 2011


[sebaygo1]


This time Max and Stacy report on American anger at gas prices, Middle East fears on wheat prices and the Chinese love for gold that has double in a year. 

In the second half of the show, Max talks to investment adviser, Ned Naylor-Leyland of Cheviot Asset Management in London, about thousand ounce silver bars and the precious metals market.
